description: Northern Lights Fund Trust IV - Long Cramer Tracker ETF is an exchange traded fund launched by Northern Lights Fund Trust IV. The fund is managed by Tuttle Capital Management, LLC. It invests in public equity markets of global region. The fund invests directly and through other funds in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund employs long/short strategy to create its portfolio. The fund invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified market capitalization. Northern Lights Fund Trust IV - Long Cramer Tracker ETF is domiciled in the United States.
name: Northern Lights Fund Trust IV - Long Cramer Tracker ETF
